sentences.sentence: The new generation of deans will undoubtedly preside over dramatic changes.
sentences.translation: 毫无疑问，新一代的头儿们引导了这个戏剧性的变化。

sentences.sentence: As the applause died down, I said, But Richard Deans story doesn't end there.
sentences.translation: 当掌声渐渐停息的时候，我说：“理查德·迪安的故事并没有在那里结束。”

sentences.sentence: In 1982, the deans of the architectural schools of the United Sates chose I.M.Pei as the best designer of significant non-residential structures.
sentences.translation: 1982年，美国建筑学校的校长评贝聿铭为出色的非居住用建筑物最杰出的设计者。
